---
title: Beef and Lentil Curry with baby spinach and rice
description: Like many North Indian dishes, this recipe relies on an expert blend of herbs and spices. The succulent beef and lentils in this dish are seasoned with a mix of fenugreek, turmeric, cayenne and ground coriander to name just a few.
